-*Razmišljam* o svim mogućim scenarijima (I'm thinking about all possible scenarios).
-*Razmišljala* sam o tome dugo (I was thinking about it for a long time).
-*Razmišljanje* o svim mogućim posljedicama nije bilo lako (Thinking about all possible consequences wasn't easy).
-*Razmišljanjima* smo se bavili nekoliko dana (We were occupied with thoughts for a few days).
-*Razmišljajući* o svim mogućim izborima, odlučili smo se za najbolju opciju (Thinking about all possible options, we decided for the best one).